Al Sahwa Schools in Muscat, Oman, were struggling to seamlessly transition between remote, hybrid, and in-person learning. Does this problem sound all too familiar? 

Watch the full video at the link in our bio to learn how Acer Chromebooks helped them bridge the gap.

In her work for @OneTreePlanted, Kyleigh uses technology and her knowledge of ecosystem health to restore areas that have been damaged by fire and drought. Discover more Barrier Breakers at the link in our bio.
Meet Antonio. He raises trees that help restore critical wildlife habitat lost to fire and drought. Get inspired by more Barrier Breakers like him at the link in our bio.
